1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:19,820
Legend of Awakening

3
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:22,579
Episode 23

4
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,520
When we arrived,

5
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,079
I found that your army

6
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:28,040
had surrounded the post.

7
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:30,720
I even didn’t know I was

8
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:31,840
in Tan or Shuo.

9
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,640
It is a routine to have army for security

10
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,720
at the peace talk site.

11
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,720
You say you come to negotiate,

12
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,079
but you actually bring an army here.

13
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,640
It seems that you don’t mean what you said.

14
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,880
Xu Tianbing,

15
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:50,360
peace talk benefits both countries and people.

16
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,160
It is the decision of majesty and your emperor.

17
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:54,800
Why?

18
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,600
Are you afraid of

19
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,800
my Longjie Army containing less than 100 people

20
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,880
because of your poor military ability?

21
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,080
Qin Qi.

22
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:04,920
General Xu.

23
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,560
Minister.

24
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,360
I didn’t mean that.

25
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,400
However, the years of war

26
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,920
only made our people suffer

27
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,000
and benefited others.

28
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,720
I also received massage saying

29
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,160
Shanhai Gang has come to E’zhou.

30
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,840
No one knows what they are up to.

31
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,560
In my opinion,

32
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:26,960
we have to be

33
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,280
careful right now.

34
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,800
Enough. General Xu.

35
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,440
Peace talk is coming. Avoid conflicting.

36
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,520
As I say, minister,

37
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:43,000
I know you

38
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:45,520
are pursuing peace between the two countries.

39
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,640
The peace talk has begun.

40
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:51,440
Your son took his friends

41
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,640
and Miss Qin

42
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,079
threatened to take my life.

43
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,000
They threatened me with peace talk

44
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,720
at the gate of my city

45
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,960
and asked me to let refugees in.

46
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,840
Minister Xu,

47
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,040
you two must have made your decision.

48
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,720
And I as a general

49
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,040
may well have to retire.

50
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,360
Please go on your talk.

51
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,120
I will leave first.

52
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,520
General Xu!

53
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:25,960
Minister Xu.

54
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:27,400
Your general may be

55
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,520
too arrogant.

56
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,040
I…

57
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,800
Minister.

58
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:33,560
My sister was indeed self-indulgent in the
refugee event.

59
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,720
Please forgive her.

60
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,800
It’s just a misunderstanding.

61
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,480
We have exchanged our peace talk contract.

62
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,840
We have some details to talk about.

63
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:45,640
Shall we call it a day?

64
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,480
Your son is upright.

65
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:49,960
Please send my best wishes to him.

66
00:04:57,360 --> 00:05:01,240
The peace talk may not seem so easy.

67
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,440
Majesty was determined

68
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,920
and asked us to make it.

69
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,200
In my opinion,

70
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,520
you have to stop your sister

71
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:12,240
from doing wrong things.

72
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:24,180
[Breeze Mansion]

73
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,480
Father,

74
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,520
why did you come?

75
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:39,640
My good son and his friends

76
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,280
kidnapped the general of this city

77
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,080
and let the refugees in.

78
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,360
If I don’t come back,

79
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,800
will you change the world one day?

80
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:47,640
Father,

81
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,840
General Xu was too cautious.

82
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,400
People are innocent.

83
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:54,159
You have come for the peace talk.

84
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,760
We have to deal with those refugees anyway.

85
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:58,320
If we take actions earlier, they will suffer less.

86
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,520
As for my friends,

87
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,520
they are my fellow disciples in Big Dipper.

88
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,680
Please let them live in here.

89
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,960
I will take care of them.

90
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,680
Weifeng, I know that you have cared about

91
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:11,080
the politics since you were young.

92
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:15,240
But you have to

93
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,880
be steadier from now on.

94
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:19,880
I am sorry.

95
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,000
I made you worry.

96
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:24,880
Forget it.

97
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,360
According to General Qin,

98
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:29,720
Shanhai Gang seems

99
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:30,920
to be ambitious.

100
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,280
They may cause big troubles.

101
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,840
It benefits us to have helpers from Jianghu.

102
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:39,159
The war has lasted for too long.

103
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,440
Anyway,

104
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:43,200
the peace talk must be made.

105
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,320
Father,

106
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,560
I told you about joining the army.

107
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:55,880
You promised me.

108
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,600
It is what I wrote about managing

109
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,080
the army during my days in Big Dipper.

110
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,920
Please have a look.

111
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,520
Since you have left Big Dipper,

112
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,440
just stay at home for your illness.

113
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,000
Don’t think about these things.

114
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,160
Don’t bother writing these.

115
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,600
I know what you are thinking of.

116
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:17,040
I know that you can’t be persuaded.

117
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,120
But you should be practical

118
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:23,560
and try to tell right from wrong.

119
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,160
I understand.

120
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:39,140
[Breeze Mansion]

121
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,560
Be practical?

122
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,120
If everyone is satisfied with
their original status,

123
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,560
and is afraid of changing,

124
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,760
who will unite the world?

125
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,240
Help yourself?

126
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:30,160
Your sister is an idiot.

127
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,669
And you ask me to help myself?

128
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,600
Who is the idiot?

129
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:45,520
Master,

130
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:47,840
what are you doing?

131
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:50,480
Didn’t you ask me to bring sugar to you?

132
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,880
I agree.

133
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,480
You are no longer an idiot.

134
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,560
I have only one condition.

135
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:02,520
Do you have medicines which can strengthen

136
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:04,240
human body and cure their illness?

137
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,840
If I have such,

138
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,480
I would have eaten myself.

139
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,640
They can’t be left.

140
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,840
Who do you want to give?

141
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,160
You know who.

142
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,520
You can give them to anyone

143
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,800
except Xu Weifeng, the toy boy.

144
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,440
Why?

145
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,160
I am not willing.

146
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,080
Master, I don’t understand.

147
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,880
Am I inferior to him?

148
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,440
You behave like a servant in front of him

149
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,080
while you are so cruel to me.

150
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,360
Master,

151
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,640
look at me.

152
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,760
I don’t have relatives working in the government

153
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:45,280
but I am the young master of Wuyou Valley.

154
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:47,200
I am rich, too.

155
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,240
And,

156
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:51,080
he must have some problems.

157
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:53,920
No one can be so perfect.

158
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,440
You won’t give me no matter what happens, right?

159
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,120
You can just give me some aliment.

160
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,720
Here.

161
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,880
Here.

162
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,160
My good disciple.

163
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:12,280
Good bye.

164
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,680
I’m sorry.

165
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:37,000
I am a little annoyed.

166
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,720
I bring you some aliment.

167
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,880
I have had in the day time.

168
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,120
It is different.

169
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,400
It can build up your body.

170
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:46,480
You can join the army after taking.

171
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,080
Have you heard the

172
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,400
conversation between my father and I?

173
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,920
By chance.

174
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,360
Don’t you want to join the army?

175
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,320
If it is effective,

176
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,360
I will ask Mo Lin for more.

177
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,360
Thank you all the same.

178
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,240
But it is useless

179
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,360
for me.

180
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:13,120
I have too many such things in my early years.

181
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:17,160
Maybe I am bound to be a waste.

182
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,280
What I wrote is just

183
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:22,200
my day dreaming.

184
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:26,320
It is not necessarily wrong to have dreams.

185
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,440
When I was young, my brother and I

186
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,640
were imprisoned in a horrible place.

187
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,800
I thought it would in my dream to get out.

188
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,040
But my brother told me

189
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,960
that have dreams were not necessarily wrong.

190
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,560
If you don’t even have your dreams,

191
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,360
you will really die.

192
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:49,560
Don’t lose hope.

193
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,200
Your advice may one day

194
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,640
be put into use one day.

195
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:57,080
Su Tang,

196
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,440
I just met you.

197
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,480
Why do you help me like that?

198
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:06,040
Both my brother and I don’t have a home.

199
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:08,440
I really hope you can succeed

200
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,280
as you helped others go home.

201
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,960
I have had asthma since young.

202
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:20,760
Even my father lost hope in me.

203
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,800
You are the first one to say it to me.

204
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:25,960
Su Tang,

205
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:28,440
thank you.

206
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,440
After senior left,

207
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,520
you are the first one

208
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,120
to cheer my brother up.

209
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,720
I thank you for him.

210
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,760
Does Lu Ping really

211
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:40,560
care about his senior?

212
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:50,280
OK. I will do it myself.

213
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:53,720
It’s late.

214
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,240
You have to go to bed.

215
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,280
I will take the medicine.

216
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:58,520
By the way,

217
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,040
send my message to Lu Ping

218
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:02,960
that his senior will surly come back.

219
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:18,800
I have taken the medicine.

220
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,280
Don’t worry.

221
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,120
Good bye.

222
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:36,880
Boss.

223
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,360
I know what you mean when you

224
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:40,720
say that I should help myself.

225
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:42,440
You toy boy,

226
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:46,480
my drugs would bring you diarrhea.

227
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,840
Let’s see how you can flirt with master.

228
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:07,280
Miss,

229
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,280
according to the general,

230
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,320
it is during the peace talk.

231
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,760
Please stay at your room.

232
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,320
Did you climb over the wall again?

233
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:23,160
Aren’t you afraid of being killed by arrows?

234
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,080
I said that we can

235
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:27,720
meet even if we don’t live together.

236
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,520
Have you got any information about Xifan?

237
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:35,820
[Breeze Mansion]

238
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,040
It is already midnight.

239
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:52,160
He hasn’t got diarrhea.

240
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:55,440
Did he find out it is a purge

241
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,400
and refused to eat?

242
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,840
He goes out alone

243
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,240
in such a night.

244
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:27,640
As I said, he can’t be so perfect.

245
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:30,000
He must have some problems.

246
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:20,960
It’s strange.

247
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,520
Where is he?

248
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:31,440
I asked the scouts your brother gave

249
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:32,840
me to search in the city for long

250
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:34,200
without results.

251
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,440
What about the peace talk?

252
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,520
It will start tomorrow.

253
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:41,720
If Shanhai Gang wants to interfere,

254
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,680
they will certainly appear tonight.

255
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:47,200
Xu Tianbing is arrogant

256
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:49,200
and made conflicts with my brother.

257
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,760
My brother tolerated him

258
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,320
for the sake of the peace talk.

259
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:59,280
He isn’t so patient

260
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,000
when facing me.

261
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,109
It is different between

262
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:06,829
sister and official affairs.

263
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,400
If one day, some brat boy

264
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:13,240
gets close to Su Tang,

265
00:17:13,829 --> 00:17:14,800
what will you do?

266
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:21,160
If Su Tang really likes him,

267
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,040
I don’t care who he is.

268
00:17:27,109 --> 00:17:29,000
Lu Ping, don’t give your sister to a bad guy.

269
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:33,560
Xu Weifeng is not a good man.

270
00:17:34,080 --> 00:17:35,160
How did you come, too?

271
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:36,400
Why?

272
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,320
Lu Ping can come.

273
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,680
Why can’t I?

274
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:39,800
What’s more,

275
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,160
I have been good at Force of Air

276
00:17:41,280 --> 00:17:42,680
since I broke my force.

277
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,920
I no longer need bricks when climbing over walls.

278
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:48,240
Oh,

279
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,000
let’s talk about something serious.

280
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,840
I saw Xu Weifeng put out the candle

281
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:53,640
and left his mansion.

282
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,640
He was stealthy.

283
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:57,760
He must have some secrets.

284
00:17:58,280 --> 00:18:00,640
But I lost him at the half way

285
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,920
or I will expose his secret.

286
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,720
Why did you stay at the gate

287
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:06,600
of his mansion at midnight?

288
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:08,160
I…

289
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:08,800
Miss,

290
