308
00:18:58,080 --> 00:18:58,640
Young master.

309
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,640
Young master.

310
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:00,520
Young master.

311
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:02,360
Mr. Xu.

