316
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:08,680
But you have to save him.

317
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:11,880
Did you give him poison?

318
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:12,760
I…

319
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,000
I just gave

