325
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,840
What was he up to?

326
00:19:25,120 --> 00:19:25,840
Young master heard that you

327
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,680
were searching for Mr. Yan.

328
00:19:27,800 --> 00:19:29,200
He gave some money

329
00:19:29,320 --> 00:19:30,080
to the refugees

330
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:32,520
to help you ask about the information.

331
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:33,880
