336
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,280
Master,

337
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:57,800
I know I am lazy, greedy and cowardly.

338
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:00,080
But I swear in my name of

339
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:00,680
the World’s No. 1 Assassin

340
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:02,400
that I didn’t give him poison.

341
00:20:03,230 --> 00:20:03,910
You would rather believe him.

342
00:20:03,910 --> 00:20:05,000
-Than believe me.
-Enough.

343
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:06,000
Mo Lin,

344
