470
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:46,960
Don’t worry.

471
00:26:47,560 --> 00:26:49,080
They are brothers.

472
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,520
They will end all the things.

473
00:27:05,800 --> 00:27:06,360
