474
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,000
You should not stand in the wind.

475
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:10,720
I will go to get you a coat.

476
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:44,240
I know I am lazy, greedy and cowardly.

477
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:46,320
But I swear in my name of

478
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:46,920
the World’s No. 1 Assassin

479
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:48,880
that I didn’t give him poison.

480
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:04,200
What?

481
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,440
People can use acupoint

482
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:08,680
