00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:55,150
let’s all go back for a rest.

579
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:56,630
When everyone is here,

580
00:34:57,160 --> 00:34:58,800
we’ll talk again.

581
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:17,020
[E’zhou Post]

582
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:38,000
I enclosed your Force of Heft using needles.

583
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,200
You can’t escape.

584
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,080
Drink. It’ll make you better.

585
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,960
Mo Lin was right.

586
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:46,000
You are a liar.

587
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:50,040
You cheated us at the beginning.

588
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:52,120
You made my brother trust you.

589
00:35:52,640 --> 00:35:54,120
My actions may be questionable

590
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:55,640
but I am not wrong.

591
00:35:56,600 --> 00:35:58,280
I did it all for Tan.

592
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:01,360
You said you would give refugees their homes.

593
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:04,920
But actually, you just want

594
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,600
a war like Shanhai Gang.

595
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:14,440
Where do refugees come from?

596
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:19,400
From the war between the two countries.

597
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:21,880
What’s the use of peace talk?

598
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:24,400
Temporary peace can’t be maintained.

599
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:27,320
Once the kings are ambitious again,

600
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:29,360
everything goes the same.

601
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,680
We can only stop war using war.

602
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:34,640
When the two countries unite,

603
00:36:35,200 --> 00:36:36,720
people will live in peace

604
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:39,400
forever.

605
00:36:41,160 --> 00:36:42,800
I have known this since my early years.

606
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:47,160
But I can’t realize it.

607
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,880
You just talk about justice

608
00:36:50,640 --> 00:36:52,200
but what you actually want is war.

609
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:56,040
That’s why you cooperate with the gang.

610
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:59,080
It does no good to Tan.

611
00:37:00,040 --> 00:37:02,040
You just do it for yourself.

612
00:37:03,240 --> 00:37:04,560
I have prepared to

613
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:06,600
write to his Majesty.

614
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,480
When the peace talk fails,

615
00:37:09,520 --> 00:37:11,800
Tan can attack together with Dan.

616
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,760
We’ll directly march to Kaifeng.

617
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:15,680
Su Tang,

618
00:37:19,640 --> 00:37:20,880
it’s you who tell me that

619
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:23,880
I can realize

620
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:26,000
my dream.

621
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:28,240
I also believe that when

622
00:37:28,680 --> 00:37:30,080
I am successful,

623
00:37:30,440 --> 00:37:32,160
you can be with me.

624
00:37:32,160 --> 00:37:33,520
You won’t.

625
00:37:36,680 --> 00:37:38,480
My brother has decided with Qin Qi

626
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:40,720
to stop Shanhai Gang from carrying out their plan.

627
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:43,160
Qin Qi.

628
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:47,560
There will be a big show in the post.

629
00:37:48,040 --> 00:37:48,800
But Lu Ping may have no

630
00:37:48,960 --> 00:37:50,560
chance to see it.

631
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:54,080
Shanhai Gang can’t help you without reason.

632
00:37:56,160 --> 00:37:57,280
They want my brother.

633
00:38:00,680 --> 00:38:02,200
You gave him to them!

634
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:03,400
Right?

635
00:38:04,560 --> 00:38:06,840
Tingsong Villa is just a trap, right?

636
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:08,480
I tell you.

637
00:38:09,040 --> 00:38:10,480
My brother is very clever.

638
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,640
You are bound to be exposed by him.

639
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:15,160
He won’t go into the trap automatically.

640
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:16,880
Lu Ping is indeed clever

641
00:38:18,120 --> 00:38:20,640
but he values friendship too much.

642
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:21,800
People like him must

643
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:25,040
be sacrificed for the whole plan.

644
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:39,520
Lu Ping.

645
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:42,040
Shanhai Gang may have their plan.

646
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:44,480
We shouldn’t be like this.

647
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:47,600
I will attract the attention of Zhou Youlong

648
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:48,800
and you can run away yourself.

649
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:49,920
Send the information to my brother.

650
00:38:50,120 --> 00:38:50,520
No.

651
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:53,360
I can’t leave you alone here.

652
00:38:53,720 --> 00:38:55,520
When they relax,

653
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:57,920
let’s take actions together.

654
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,080
We will act according to the situation.

655
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,360
The person who can save you has come.

656
00:39:13,640 --> 00:39:14,280
Mo…

657
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:18,040
You still talk so much when you are dying?

658
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:21,040
It sucks to see couples.

659
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:23,720
What about using the Method of Xi Sui

660
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:27,400
on this girl for me?

661
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:28,760
Master Zhou.

662
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:31,680
How does it feel to have Yan Xifan as your boss?

663
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:35,640
Just a betrayer kicked out of his home.

664
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:37,520
How can you compare him with me?

665
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:39,640
But you are actually

666
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:42,040
doing things for him.

667
00:39:43,040 --> 00:39:44,800
You have not stayed in the gang for long.

668
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:48,080
Wen Gecheng died and Yan Xifan came.

669
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:50,840
You are always a subordinate.

670
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:52,760
What do you mean?

671
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,720
Didn’t Lin Tianyi tell you?

672
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:57,280
I am the awakening with six forces in my body.

673
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:59,280
I am the best material for Xi Sui.

674
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:01,560
If you send me back to the gang,

675
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:04,200
you can share the award with Yan Xifan.

676
00:40:04,640 --> 00:40:06,320
It can’t be much.

677
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:08,360
But if you get my six forces,

678
00:40:09,240 --> 00:40:11,480
you can be carefree ever since.

679
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,760
You don’t have to be an idiot

680
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:15,520
who is always listening to others.

681
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:18,320
Do you really agree?

682
00:40:21,600 --> 00:40:22,640
Xifan has said that

683
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:24,040
I am too kind.

684
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:26,640
Let Qin Sang go

685
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:28,280
and I will agree.

686
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:31,120
You want to sacrifice your martial arts

687
00:40:32,080 --> 00:40:33,960
just for a girl?

688
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:36,440
I really overestimated you.

689
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:37,440
Lu Ping,

690
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:38,640
are you kidding?

691
00:40:39,240 --> 00:40:40,440
I am just an ordinary man.

692
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:43,800
If you are hurt because of me,

693
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:45,600
I can’t be at ease.

694
00:40:48,280 --> 00:40:49,080
Zhou Youlong.

695
00:40:50,200 --> 00:40:51,360
The girl I love

696
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:54,720
must be safe and live long.

697
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,720
I can sacrifice my life

698
00:40:58,600 --> 00:41:00,120
for her,

699
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:01,680
let alone my martial arts.

700
00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:05,760
It would be better if you

701
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:09,160
kill Yan Xifan for me

702
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,920
after you improve your skills.

703
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,040
Master Zhou,

704
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:16,560
you can’t betray Master Lin.

705
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,600
Zhou Youlong,

706
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:21,920
dare you to touch him!

707
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,040
I will kill you.

708
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,320
Master,

709
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,040
let’s talk at another place.

710
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:28,440
I can’t stand the scene

711
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:29,480
of saying goodbye.

712
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:31,800
We have to focus when doing Xi Sui.

713
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:08,400
As I said,

714
00:42:08,640 --> 00:42:09,680
you can’t leave me.

715
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,040
Are you OK?

716
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:30,120
I’m OK.

717
00:42:32,600 --> 00:42:35,560
Just now, you said you like me

718
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:37,840
and could sacrifice your life for me.

719
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:39,600
Is it true or were you acting?

720
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,840
I will tell you after all these.

721
00:42:47,200 --> 00:42:47,800
Boss, please flirt

722
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:50,360
at another time.

723
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:52,440
I found our senior in the city.

724
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:53,680
He dressed like another person

725
00:42:53,880 --> 00:42:54,600
and sneaked into the post.

726
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:56,520
There were many baskets on the cart beside,

727
00:42:56,680 --> 00:42:58,360
with a strong smell of blood.

728
00:42:58,560 --> 00:42:59,200
It felt strange.

729
00:42:59,400 --> 00:43:00,600
So I came to you.

730
00:43:01,120 --> 00:43:01,920
Post?

731
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:03,440
What was he doing there?

732
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:04,560
Oh dear.

733
00:43:05,640 --> 00:43:07,400
Shanhai Gang will ruin the peace talk.

734
00:43:08,160 --> 00:43:09,880
Qin Qi is very careful about this.

735
00:43:10,680 --> 00:43:12,160
Now Xifan interfered into it.

736
00:43:13,160 --> 00:43:14,320
It will cause great trouble.

